# Component Patterns

## Buttons
- **ALL buttons: `variant="outline"`** - no solid buttons
- Edit buttons: `variant="outline" size="sm"` with icon + text
- Icons use `mr-2` before text

## Layout
- No Card components - use `<Separator class="my-8" />` between sections
- Full-width pages - no `max-w-*` constraints (except auth pages)
- Left-aligned content - no `text-center`

## Sheet/Drawer Editing
- Click item â†’ Opens Sheet from right
- Sheet contains form with `py-6 px-1` padding
- Save/Cancel in Sheet footer
- NEVER use inline editing or separate edit pages

## Lists
- Always show empty state
- Always show loading skeleton
- Use shared components: `NetCard`, `OperatorCard`
- Grid: `grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-3`
- Empty state: `py-8 text-center` with muted text

## Filter Bars
- Search input: `w-full sm:flex-1 sm:max-w-xs` with `pl-9` for icon
- Select filters: `flex-1 sm:flex-none sm:w-[WIDTH]` (120px-180px)
- Container: `flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2`
- Action buttons: `hidden lg:flex ml-auto gap-2` (hidden on mobile)

## Pagination
- Always use "Load More" pattern, never numbered pagination
- Button: `w-full lg:w-auto lg:px-8`
- Container: `pt-4 pb-16 lg:pb-0` (extra bottom padding for mobile FAB)
- Show only when `hasMore && !isLoading`

## Mobile FAB (Floating Action Button)
- Position: `fixed bottom-20 right-4`
- Size: `h-14 w-14 rounded-full`
- Style: `shadow-lg z-40 bg-background`
- Visibility: `lg:hidden` (only on mobile)
- Only for create actions

## Section Headers
- Style: `text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2`
- Icon: `h-4 w-4`
- Margin: `mb-4` for content below

## Section Separators
- Always: `<Separator class="my-8" />` between major sections
- Never use Card components as separators

## Confirmations
- Use AlertDialog for destructive actions
- Use Toast for success/info messages